                A small step from the end of every Indian citizen can be a big step for fulfilling the purpose of the Narendra Modi’s ‘Clean India’ campaign.
            </div>

            <div class="button-container">
                <div class="input-group">
                    <form class="custom-file" method="get" action="/requestSubmission">
